# KnowledgeBot 🤖  

A conversational knowledge assistant built with **Java** and **Gradle**.  
KnowledgeBot leverages rule-based policies (`policies.json`) and a client integration layer to provide interactive responses.  

---

## 🚀 Features
- Conversational AI backend
- Configurable policies (`src/main/resources/policies.json`)
- Gradle build system for easy setup & dependencies
- Modular design for future extensions
- Demo video included

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Java 17+**
- **Gradle** (Kotlin DSL)
- **GSON / JSON Processing** (if policies parsing is used)

---

## ⚙️ Setup & Run

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/mohsinjaved1165/AI-Initiative---KnowledgeBot.git
cd AI-Initiative---KnowledgeBot

./gradlew clean run --args="How many paternity leave are there for employees?"
./gradlew clean run --args="How many paid leaves do we get per year?"

  ---

##  Build the project
./gradlew build


  ---
## Run the application
./gradlew run


  --

##  Demo

A short demonstration of KnowledgeBot is included in docs folder
